title: Grateful Dead Live at Fillmore West on 1971-07-02
description:
Set 1

Bertha, Me And Bobby McGee, Next Time You See Me, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Playin' In The Band, Loser, The Rub, Me & My Uncle, Big Railroad Blues, Hard To Handle, Deal, Promised Land, Good Lovin'

Set 2

Sugar Magnolia, Sing Me Back Home, Mama Tried, Cryptical Envelopement-> Drums-> The Other One, Big Boss Man, Casey Jones, Not Fade Away-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Not Fade Away, E: Johnny B. Goode

'That's It For The Other One' dedicated to Owsley - Other artist(s): GD; NRPS; Rowan Brothers lost Grateful Dead Fillmore West show FM broodcast KSAN-San Francisco, KSFX-San Fr~isco. and KMET}*

reviews.review_text:
50 years ago today ! thanks to all involved for this beautiful restoration. 
every tuning note, DJ comment and audience demand is engraved in my brain from those tapes from long ago. i just wish i could have seen that guy's face when they finally pull out Johnny B Goode at the very end !
